To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private Kicking _kicking;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_kicking = Kicking(symbol);

// In OnData()
if (_kicking.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "kicking", _kicking.Current.Value);
}
